<tool id="SAGA.grid_spline.5" name="Multilevel B-Spline from Grid Points" version="1.0.0"><description>Multilevel B-spline algorithm for spatial interpolation of scattered data as proposed by Lee, Wolberg and Shin (1997). The algorithm makes use of a coarse-to-fine hierarchy of control lattices to generate a sequence of bicubic B-spline functions, whose sum approaches the desired interpolation function. Large performance gains are realized by using B-spline refinement to reduce the sum of these functions into one equivalent B-spline function. &amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;The 'Maximum Level' determines the maximum size of the final B-spline matrix and increases exponential with each level. Where level=10 requires about 1mb level=12 needs about 16mb and level=14 about 256mb(!) of additional memory. </description><inputs><param name="GRID" label="Grid" help="Grid" type="text" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="TARGET_DEFINITION" label="Target Grid System" help="Target Grid System" type="text" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="TARGET_USER_SIZE" label="Cellsize" help="Cellsize" type="float" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="TARGET_USER_XMIN" label="West" help="West" type="float" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="TARGET_USER_XMAX" label="East" help="East" type="float" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="TARGET_USER_YMIN" label="South" help="South" type="float" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="TARGET_USER_YMAX" label="North" help="North" type="float" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="TARGET_USER_COLS" label="Columns" help="Number of cells in East-West direction." type="integer" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="TARGET_USER_ROWS" label="Rows" help="Number of cells in North-South direction." type="integer" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="TARGET_USER_FITS" label="Fit" help="Fit" type="text" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="TARGET_TEMPLATE" label="Target System" help="use this grid's system for output grids" type="text" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="METHOD" label="Refinement" help="Refinement" type="text" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="EPSILON" label="Threshold Error" help="Threshold Error" type="float" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="LEVEL_MAX" label="Maximum Level" help="Maximum Level" type="integer" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="UPDATE" label="Update View" help="Update View" type="boolean" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="DATATYPE" label="Data Type" help="Data Type" type="text" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /></inputs><outputs><data name="TARGET_OUT_GRID" label="Target Grid" /></outputs></tool>